,
									"text" : "You can specifiy what kind of output you would like when regressing from a given input. By default you get an iterated output that sends out key-value pairs which can be sent directly to synthesis algorithms. You may instead want a laced list where all key-value pairs are combined into a single list (useful when you want to trigger an envelope *after* inference) and finally as a rawlist where only the regressed values are output as a single list."
								}

